instructions:
If you are playing on a computer:
- Click on an item with the mouse;
- Hold down the mouse key and drag the item to the desired location.
If you are playing on a smartphone:
- Tap the item with your finger;
- Hold your finger on the touchscreen and drag the item to the desired location.
There are also 3 boosters available to you:
- Hint (light bulb icon). Sets the item to its correct location;
- Freeze. Freezes the timer for 60 seconds;
- Compass. Will show the location of any 4 items.

